        <h1 class="text-shadow">HATTERS GONNA HAT</h1>
        <h2>Find the hat you deserve.</h2>
    </header>
    <section class="container">
        <div class="d-flex text-center flex-column justify-content-center align-items-center">
            <h2>Welcome to Hatters Gonna Hat.</h2>
            <div>
                <p>At Hatters Gonna Hat, we make the highest quality hats for you. Chenipan silk, kangaroo fur and
                    guinea pig leather. We have selected the best materials to satisfy you. We have recruited the
                    best tanners and dressmakers in the region to offer the best quality to the best people : those
                    who can afford our work. You.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    <section class="container-fluid d-flex hats">
